BITCOIN DOUBLER – HOW DOES IT WORK?

[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text text_orientation=”justified” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

Bitcoin Doubler is a fully automated Bitcoin investment platform operating with no human intervention. Take full advantage of our fast and legit Bitcoin doubler platform. Our automated system gathers information from the blockchain transfers and cryptocurrency exchanges to study and predict the Bitcoin price. Our servers open and close thousands of transactions per minute, analyzing the price difference and transaction fees, and use that information to double your Bitcoins. Our data centers are located on multiple locations around the world so that our system has 100% uptime guaranteed.

FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS (FAQ)

[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row parallax_method_1=”off” background_position_1=”top_left” background_repeat_1=”no-repeat” disabled_on=”off|off|” admin_label=”row” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”][et_pb_column type=”1_2″ _builder_version=”3.0.47″ parallax=”off” parallax_method=”off” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”no-repeat”][et_pb_toggle title=”Why invest with Bitcoin?” admin_label=”Why invest with Bitcoin?” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

When you invest with Bitcoin, there are multiple benefits:

  • Transparency (you stay completely anonymous).
  • Easy to make transactions with low fee’s.
  • Bitcoin is constantly growing in volume and price, so while you are multiplying your BTC it’s value is growing as well.

[/et_pb_toggle][et_pb_toggle title=”Is your system and website safe?” admin_label=”Is your system and website safe?” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

Our data centers are located on multiple locations around the world to make sure that our system has 100% uptime.

Our webiste is CDN powered, SSL secured and protected against DDoS attacks to make sure that your stay on our website is completely safe.

[/et_pb_toggle][et_pb_toggle title=”Can I make more than one investment?” disabled_on=”off|off|off” admin_label=”Can I make more than one investment?” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

Yes, you can make as many investments as you like using our Bitcoin doubler.

[/et_pb_toggle][et_pb_toggle title=”Will my deposit appear in the recent transactions table?” disabled_on=”off|off|off” admin_label=”Will my deposit appear in the most recent transactions table?” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

Yes, your deposit will appear in the “MOST RECENT TRANSACTIONS” table after 1 confirmation from the network.

[/et_pb_toggle][et_pb_toggle title=”What are the investment limits?” disabled_on=”off|off|off” admin_label=”What are the investment limits?” _builder_version=”3.0.64″ background_size=”initial” background_position=”top_left” background_repeat=”repeat”]

There is a 0.005 BTC minimum and 10 BTC maximum limit for investments on Bitcoin Doubler.
